{"about_the_game":"Pixel-style level puzzle game, focusing on exploration and collection, regular game?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMain content: 4 style environment scenes, composed of 50 levels, jungle, desert, etc., all original, each level has a different entertainment experience;<br />\r\nAfter continuous collection, you can unlock new characters and discover many hidden elements and hidden clues in the level;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou can see from the picture that it is not beautiful, yes, all the design and production are done by one person, and one person's spare time. I apologize for not being a good experience, because I will spend all my time on the level rhythm and process design.<br />\r\nAt first I designed more than 70 levels, of which 20 were not satisfied and gave up.<br />\r\nIf you only look at this game from the appearance, it is only an appearance, and the hidden designs and easter eggs will subvert your perception of the game. I hope that the more than 50 levels I designed can convey the fun and new ideas of designing games. Games are also a way and a tool to express ideas. The ultimate goal is to communicate.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nI hope you can find the easter eggs after a few failures. The implication is that failure is also a kind of achievement and experience, and the spirit of not giving up.<br />\r\nwish you a happy life!","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"\u5192\u9669\u5bb6","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2067670/af8d8d34ef5119e6442f54fd5c59c12d78462199.jpg"},{"name":"\u661f\u661f\u4e4b\u706b","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2067670/c0fcd6c9f3d21c22c83b2fb8fe895d7e73467114.jpg"},{"name":"\u5192\u9669\u738b","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2067670/40b337a48885fb329a4a0b8ae513ea41bf301a7c.jpg"},{"name":"\u89e3\u5bc6\u9ad8\u624b","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2067670/5